data C'gsl_sf_mathieu_workspace = C'gsl_sf_mathieu_workspace{
  c'gsl_sf_mathieu_workspace'size :: CSize,
  c'gsl_sf_mathieu_workspace'even_order :: CSize,
  c'gsl_sf_mathieu_workspace'odd_order :: CSize,
  c'gsl_sf_mathieu_workspace'extra_values :: CInt,
  c'gsl_sf_mathieu_workspace'qa :: CDouble,
  c'gsl_sf_mathieu_workspace'qb :: CDouble,
  c'gsl_sf_mathieu_workspace'aa :: Ptr CDouble,
  c'gsl_sf_mathieu_workspace'bb :: Ptr CDouble,
  c'gsl_sf_mathieu_workspace'dd :: Ptr CDouble,
  c'gsl_sf_mathieu_workspace'ee :: Ptr CDouble,
  c'gsl_sf_mathieu_workspace'tt :: Ptr CDouble,
  c'gsl_sf_mathieu_workspace'e2 :: Ptr CDouble,
  c'gsl_sf_mathieu_workspace'zz :: Ptr CDouble,
  c'gsl_sf_mathieu_workspace'eval :: Ptr C'gsl_vector,
  c'gsl_sf_mathieu_workspace'evec :: Ptr C'gsl_matrix,
  c'gsl_sf_mathieu_workspace'wmat :: Ptr C'gsl_eigen_symmv_workspace
} deriving (Eq,Show)
p'gsl_sf_mathieu_workspace'size p = plusPtr p 0
p'gsl_sf_mathieu_workspace'size :: Ptr (C'gsl_sf_mathieu_workspace) -> Ptr (CSize)
p'gsl_sf_mathieu_workspace'even_order p = plusPtr p 8
p'gsl_sf_mathieu_workspace'even_order :: Ptr (C'gsl_sf_mathieu_workspace) -> Ptr (CSize)
p'gsl_sf_mathieu_workspace'odd_order p = plusPtr p 16
p'gsl_sf_mathieu_workspace'odd_order :: Ptr (C'gsl_sf_mathieu_workspace) -> Ptr (CSize)
p'gsl_sf_mathieu_workspace'extra_values p = plusPtr p 24
p'gsl_sf_mathieu_workspace'extra_values :: Ptr (C'gsl_sf_mathieu_workspace) -> Ptr (CInt)
p'gsl_sf_mathieu_workspace'qa p = plusPtr p 32
p'gsl_sf_mathieu_workspace'qa :: Ptr (C'gsl_sf_mathieu_workspace) -> Ptr (CDouble)
p'gsl_sf_mathieu_workspace'qb p = plusPtr p 40
p'gsl_sf_mathieu_workspace'qb :: Ptr (C'gsl_sf_mathieu_workspace) -> Ptr (CDouble)
p'gsl_sf_mathieu_workspace'aa p = plusPtr p 48
p'gsl_sf_mathieu_workspace'aa :: Ptr (C'gsl_sf_mathieu_workspace) -> Ptr (Ptr CDouble)
p'gsl_sf_mathieu_workspace'bb p = plusPtr p 56
p'gsl_sf_mathieu_workspace'bb :: Ptr (C'gsl_sf_mathieu_workspace) -> Ptr (Ptr CDouble)
p'gsl_sf_mathieu_workspace'dd p = plusPtr p 64
p'gsl_sf_mathieu_workspace'dd :: Ptr (C'gsl_sf_mathieu_workspace) -> Ptr (Ptr CDouble)
p'gsl_sf_mathieu_workspace'ee p = plusPtr p 72
p'gsl_sf_mathieu_workspace'ee :: Ptr (C'gsl_sf_mathieu_workspace) -> Ptr (Ptr CDouble)
p'gsl_sf_mathieu_workspace'tt p = plusPtr p 80
p'gsl_sf_mathieu_workspace'tt :: Ptr (C'gsl_sf_mathieu_workspace) -> Ptr (Ptr CDouble)
p'gsl_sf_mathieu_workspace'e2 p = plusPtr p 88
p'gsl_sf_mathieu_workspace'e2 :: Ptr (C'gsl_sf_mathieu_workspace) -> Ptr (Ptr CDouble)
p'gsl_sf_mathieu_workspace'zz p = plusPtr p 96
p'gsl_sf_mathieu_workspace'zz :: Ptr (C'gsl_sf_mathieu_workspace) -> Ptr (Ptr CDouble)
p'gsl_sf_mathieu_workspace'eval p = plusPtr p 104
p'gsl_sf_mathieu_workspace'eval :: Ptr (C'gsl_sf_mathieu_workspace) -> Ptr (Ptr C'gsl_vector)
p'gsl_sf_mathieu_workspace'evec p = plusPtr p 112
p'gsl_sf_mathieu_workspace'evec :: Ptr (C'gsl_sf_mathieu_workspace) -> Ptr (Ptr C'gsl_matrix)
p'gsl_sf_mathieu_workspace'wmat p = plusPtr p 120
p'gsl_sf_mathieu_workspace'wmat :: Ptr (C'gsl_sf_mathieu_workspace) -> Ptr (Ptr C'gsl_eigen_symmv_workspace)
instance Storable C'gsl_sf_mathieu_workspace where
  sizeOf _ = 128
  alignment _ = 8
  peek p = do
    v0 <- peekByteOff p 0
    v1 <- peekByteOff p 8
    v2 <- peekByteOff p 16
    v3 <- peekByteOff p 24
    v4 <- peekByteOff p 32
    v5 <- peekByteOff p 40
    v6 <- peekByteOff p 48
    v7 <- peekByteOff p 56
    v8 <- peekByteOff p 64
    v9 <- peekByteOff p 72
    v10 <- peekByteOff p 80
    v11 <- peekByteOff p 88
    v12 <- peekByteOff p 96
    v13 <- peekByteOff p 104
    v14 <- peekByteOff p 112
    v15 <- peekByteOff p 120
    return $ C'gsl_sf_mathieu_workspace v0 v1 v2 v3 v4 v5 v6 v7 v8 v9 v10 v11 v12 v13 v14 v15
  poke p (C'gsl_sf_mathieu_workspace v0 v1 v2 v3 v4 v5 v6 v7 v8 v9 v10 v11 v12 v13 v14 v15) = do
    pokeByteOff p 0 v0
    pokeByteOff p 8 v1
    pokeByteOff p 16 v2
    pokeByteOff p 24 v3
    pokeByteOff p 32 v4
    pokeByteOff p 40 v5
    pokeByteOff p 48 v6
    pokeByteOff p 56 v7
    pokeByteOff p 64 v8
    pokeByteOff p 72 v9
    pokeByteOff p 80 v10
    pokeByteOff p 88 v11
    pokeByteOff p 96 v12
    pokeByteOff p 104 v13
    pokeByteOff p 112 v14
    pokeByteOff p 120 v15
    return ()

data C'gsl_sf_result = C'gsl_sf_result{
  c'gsl_sf_result'val :: CDouble,
  c'gsl_sf_result'err :: CDouble
} deriving (Eq,Show)
p'gsl_sf_result'val p = plusPtr p 0
p'gsl_sf_result'val :: Ptr (C'gsl_sf_result) -> Ptr (CDouble)
p'gsl_sf_result'err p = plusPtr p 8
p'gsl_sf_result'err :: Ptr (C'gsl_sf_result) -> Ptr (CDouble)
instance Storable C'gsl_sf_result where
  sizeOf _ = 16
  alignment _ = 8
  peek p = do
    v0 <- peekByteOff p 0
    v1 <- peekByteOff p 8
    return $ C'gsl_sf_result v0 v1
  poke p (C'gsl_sf_result v0 v1) = do
    pokeByteOff p 0 v0
    pokeByteOff p 8 v1
    return ()

data C'gsl_sf_result_e10 = C'gsl_sf_result_e10{
  c'gsl_sf_result_e10'val :: CDouble,
  c'gsl_sf_result_e10'err :: CDouble,
  c'gsl_sf_result_e10'e10 :: CInt
} deriving (Eq,Show)
p'gsl_sf_result_e10'val p = plusPtr p 0
p'gsl_sf_result_e10'val :: Ptr (C'gsl_sf_result_e10) -> Ptr (CDouble)
p'gsl_sf_result_e10'err p = plusPtr p 8
p'gsl_sf_result_e10'err :: Ptr (C'gsl_sf_result_e10) -> Ptr (CDouble)
p'gsl_sf_result_e10'e10 p = plusPtr p 16
p'gsl_sf_result_e10'e10 :: Ptr (C'gsl_sf_result_e10) -> Ptr (CInt)
instance Storable C'gsl_sf_result_e10 where
  sizeOf _ = 24
  alignment _ = 8
  peek p = do
    v0 <- peekByteOff p 0
    v1 <- peekByteOff p 8
    v2 <- peekByteOff p 16
    return $ C'gsl_sf_result_e10 v0 v1 v2
  poke p (C'gsl_sf_result_e10 v0 v1 v2) = do
    pokeByteOff p 0 v0
    pokeByteOff p 8 v1
    pokeByteOff p 16 v2
    return ()
